description: Welcome to 14 Atlantic Street, Unit 2, where you'll discover a charming condo featuring three spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms, all within 1,077 sq. ft. of living space. The bedrooms are thoughtfully positioned upstairs, ensuring privacy away from the main living and kitchen areas. The kitchen seamlessly flows into the living space, creating an ideal setting for entertaining guests. Enjoy relaxing on your own expansive private deck, accessible directly from the kitchen. Situated near the soon-to-be revamped Thomas Park and the bustling shops and restaurants of Southie, this home offers the perfect opportunity to experience the vibrant neighborhood and its array of amenities. Don't miss out on this Boston treasure! Offers Due by May 5th 5 PM
